<para>Flash is not supported by the iOS platform</para>
</listitem>
<listitem>
<para>Flash and Silverlight are proprietary technologies.</para>
</listitem>
<listitem>
<para>All three techniques present accessibility challenges</para>
</listitem>
</itemizedlist>
